data.description: Welcome home! This beautiful end unit condo features 2 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms with an open floor plan. Entry level leads you to the garage and stairs up to the second floor. This floor includes your kitchen, living area, dining, a balcony and a half bath, perfect for entertaining. The stairs leading up to the third floor leads to a private oasis that opens up to two bedrooms, both with private bathrooms and the laundry room. Outside features street parking out front and garage and driveway space out back. Make this condo yours today!
